u2019s \u201cnasty remarks\u201d are in a crew environment, and whether his weak memory for numbers has ever led to safety\u2011critical errors.\n- **What would change my vote:** Credible evidence that B\u2019s interpersonal remarks are persistent and crew\u2011destabilizing, or strong evidence that another candidate (e.g., D) has substantially fewer cooperation issues while still meeting all technical and reliability requirements.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
